You get under the left side of the
transmission and there will be a 17mm
allen head filler plug on the side and
one on the bottom.  Unscrew the one on the side 
and top it off with 90 weight transmission oil
they come in squeeze bottles.
I have to top mine off every couple of weeks.
keep it full and you'll be ok.
willis 

